So you have that,
and then you also

00:38:25.320 --> 00:38:34.030 align:middle line:84%
have the relation
that the ur dagger k--

00:38:34.030 --> 00:38:37.570 align:middle line:84%
so because everything is
on-shell so in principle,

00:38:37.570 --> 00:38:38.650 align:middle line:90%
I can only--

