00:40:10.030 --> 00:40:13.870 align:middle line:90%
And so I will not go into that.

00:40:13.870 --> 00:40:18.080 align:middle line:84%
But actually, more remarkably,
those expressions--

00:40:18.080 --> 00:40:21.370 align:middle line:84%
so when we derive
this expression,

00:40:21.370 --> 00:40:25.300 align:middle line:84%
