00:40:25.300 --> 00:40:27.380 align:middle line:90%
It depends on the explicit form.

00:40:27.380 --> 00:40:29.400 align:middle line:84%
So those expressions
depend on explicit form

00:40:29.400 --> 00:40:30.800 align:middle line:90%
of these gamma matrices.

00:40:30.800 --> 00:40:33.590 align:middle line:84%
So if you have a different
set of gamma matrices,

00:40:33.590 --> 00:40:35.470 align:middle line:90%
then you get different forms.

00:40:35.470 --> 00:40:39.080 align:middle line:84%
But of course, physically,
