and here by star star.

00:41:02.220 --> 00:41:06.150 align:middle line:90%


00:41:06.150 --> 00:41:27.810 align:middle line:84%
So star and star are actually
independent of choice

00:41:27.810 --> 00:41:31.235 align:middle line:84%
