of gamma matrices.

00:41:31.235 --> 00:41:34.790 align:middle line:90%


00:41:34.790 --> 00:41:40.290 align:middle line:84%
So they're actually universal
for any choice of matrices.

00:41:40.290 --> 00:41:44.240 align:middle line:84%
So this is very useful because
when you do calculations,

00:41:44.240 --> 00:41:48.770 align:middle line:84%
then you don't have to worry
about which choice of gamma

00:41:48.770 --> 00:41:53.572 align:middle line:84%
