00:42:15.650 --> 00:42:18.620 align:middle line:84%
and the general properties
of gamma matrices

00:42:18.620 --> 00:42:23.120 align:middle line:84%
without using explicit
representations.

00:42:23.120 --> 00:42:23.980 align:middle line:90%
Yes?

